thread.title: Aid trucks bound for eastern Ghouta stripped of some medical supplies

title: Aid trucks bound for eastern Ghouta stripped of some medical supplies
text:
Aid trucks bound for eastern Ghouta stripped of some medical supplies Monday, March 05, 2018 - 00:46 
The World Health Orgaanization says Syrian government authorities have stripped most medical supplies from a U.N. aid convoy heading towards the besieged eastern Ghouta. Rough cut (no reporter narration).
